    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty\u2014it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's basically in perfect shape. No scratches, no spills, and it still has that fresh, new car smell. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for a ride that's been totally pampered and is ready for a new home, this is the one. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
