    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and made sure every single detail is perfect. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
